---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Continuum reverberation mapping";
import WikiLink from '../../components/WikiLink.astro';
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">Continuum reverberation mapping</h1>

    <p>Continuum reverberation uses inter-band time delays to probe the size and temperature structure of AGN accretion disks. Observed delays often exceed thin-disk predictions, giving rise to the "disk-size problem".</p>

    <h2>Relevant papers</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/steyn_2026_continuum_reverberation" text="Steyn et al. (2026)" /> — Large-sample analysis showing persistent disk-size discrepancy and diffuse-emission contamination.</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Base>
